Name:		gq
Version:	0.2.3
Release:	1
License:	GPL
Group:		Networking/Utilities
Group(pl):	Sieciowe/Narzêdzia
Source0:	http://download.sourceforge.net/gqclient/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
